<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            color: black;
            background-color: #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #eee; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#eee" style="background-color: #eee;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="500" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#fff" style="background-color: #fff; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="background-color: #02001e; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                            {{>header}}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border-top: 1px solid #4338ca; padding: 15px 15px 0;">
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: bolder; text-align: left;">
                                {{ title }}
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 15px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #4338ca;">
                            <p style="margin: 0;">
                                You've initiated a claim request on <b>{{ amount }} {{ tokenSymbol }}</b> sent you using the following address:
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin-top:5px; background-color: #eee; padding:10px; font-size: 14px; border:1px solid #eee;">Address: {{ wallet }}</p>
                            <p style="font-weight: bolder; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                                Verification code:
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: bolder; color: #4338ca;">
                                {{ code }}
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;">The verification code will expire after 10 minutes. Do not share your code with anyone.</p>
                            <p style="font-weight: bolder; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                                Security tips
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Be aware of phishing sites and always verify sources with <b><a href="https://dexapay.com" style="color: #4338ca;">Dexa Pay</a></b></li>
                                <li>No Dexa Pay staff will ask you for your secret code.</li>
                                <li>To stay secure, setup your app authentication here</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>
                                Don't recognize this activity? Please <a href="" style="color: #4338ca;">lock your funds</a> and contact <a href="" style="color: #4338ca;">customer support</a> immediately.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-size: 13px;">
                                <em>This is an automated email, please do not reply to it.</em>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            {{>footer}}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
